org.md2k.datakitapi.source.platform

Class PlatformType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.md2k.datakitapi.source.platform.PlatformType

  • public class PlatformType
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides constants used for indicating the type of device being used as a data source.

    Available types are:

    • AutoSense Chest
    • AutoSense Bluetooth Low Energy
    • AutoSense Wrist
    • Microsoft Band
    • Phone
    • Omron Blood Pressure
    • Omron Weight Scale
    • Easysense
    • MotionSense
    • Oral-B Toothbrush
    • MotionSense with Heart Rate Variability
    • RF Beacon (iBeacon)
